56 void GeometricKinematicCommander::statemachineThread(const ros::TimerEvent& event)
57 {
58  masterslave::OpenIGTLStateService stateStringMsg;
59  if(newState!=state)
60  {
61  switch(newState)
62  {
63  case IDLE:
64  if(stateService.exists()) stateStringMsg.request.state = "Idle;";
65  state = newState;
66  break;
67  case FREE:
68  if(stateService.exists()) stateStringMsg.request.state = "Free;";
69  state = newState;
70  break;
71  case MOVE_TO_POSE:
72  if(stateService.exists()) stateStringMsg.request.state = "MoveToPose;rob;";
73  state = newState;
74  break;
75  }
76  }
77  if(stateService.exists())
78  {
79  stateService.call(stateStringMsg);
80  statemachineIsRunning = stateStringMsg.response.alive;
81  ROS_DEBUG_STREAM("Service Call: alive: " << statemachineIsRunning);
82  }
83 }

119 void GeometricKinematicCommander::loop()
120 {
121  double lastTime = ros::Time::now().toSec();
122  masterslave::GeometricKinematicRCM rcmService;
123  tf::poseEigenToMsg(startPositionLBR,rcmService.request.T_0_FL);
124  rcmClient.call(rcmService);
125 
126  masterslave::GeometricKinematicDirectKinematics directKinematicsService;
127  std::vector<double> jointAngles(jointAnglesAct.data(),jointAnglesAct.data()+jointAnglesAct.rows());
128  directKinematicsService.request.jointAngles = jointAngles;
129  tf::poseEigenToMsg(startPositionLBR,rcmService.request.T_0_FL);
130  directKinematicsClient.call(directKinematicsService);
131 
132  ros::Rate rate(rosRate);
133  while(ros::ok())
134  {
135  ros::spinOnce();
136  cycleTime = ros::Time::now().toSec() - lastTime;
137  lastTime = ros::Time::now().toSec();
138 
139  // Hier muss der TCP-Service gecallt werden
140  masterslave::Manipulation manipulationService;
141  tf::poseEigenToMsg(TCP,manipulationService.request.T_0_EE_old);
142  tcpClient.call(manipulationService);
143  tf::poseMsgToEigen(manipulationService.response.T_0_EE_new,TCP);
144 
145  masterslave::GeometricKinematicInverseKinematics inverseKinematicsService;
146  tf::poseEigenToMsg(TCP, inverseKinematicsService.request.T_0_EE);
147  inverseKinematicsClient.call(inverseKinematicsService);
148  tf::poseMsgToEigen(inverseKinematicsService.response.T_0_FL,T_0_FL);
149  lbrTargetPositionPub.publish(inverseKinematicsService.response.T_0_FL);
150  jointAnglesTar = Eigen::VectorXd::Map(inverseKinematicsService.response.jointAnglesTarget.data(),inverseKinematicsService.response.jointAnglesTarget.size());
151  rate.sleep();
152  }
153 }

204 void GeometricKinematicCommander::calcQ6()
205 {
206  jointAnglesAct(2) = (motorAngles(4) + motorAngles(3)) / 2;
207 
208  if(fabs(motorAngles(4) + motorAngles(3))<0)
209  gripper_stop = true;
210  else
211  gripper_stop = false;

214 void GeometricKinematicCommander::commandVelocities()
215 {
216  double gripperVelocity;
217  std_msgs::Float64 Q4Vel, Q5Vel, Q6nVel, Q6pVel;
218  Q4Vel.data = (jointAnglesTar(0) - jointAnglesAct(0))/cycleTime;
219  Q5Vel.data = (jointAnglesTar(1) - jointAnglesAct(1))/cycleTime;
220  if(gripper_close && !gripper_open && !gripper_stop)
221  {
222  gripperVelocity = gripperVelocityValue;
223  }
224  else if(gripper_open && !gripper_close && !gripper_stop)
225  {
226  gripperVelocity = -gripperVelocityValue;
227  }
228  else
229  {
230  gripperVelocity = 0;
231  }
232 
233  Q6nVel.data = (jointAnglesTar(2)-jointAnglesAct(2))/cycleTime;
234  Q6pVel.data = (jointAnglesTar(2)-jointAnglesAct(2))/cycleTime;
235  // Stoppen der Greiferbacken, wenn eine der beiden am Anschlag ist, um Greiferöffnungswinkel nicht zu ändern
236  if(motorAngles(4)>=0.95*M_PI && (jointAnglesTar(2)-jointAnglesAct(2))>0)
237  {
238  Q6nVel.data = 0;
239  }
240  if(motorAngles(3)<=-0.95*M_PI && (jointAnglesTar(2)-jointAnglesAct(2))<0)
241  {
242  Q6pVel.data = 0;
243  }
244 
245  Q6nVel.data += gripperVelocity/cycleTime;
246  Q6pVel.data -= gripperVelocity/cycleTime;
247 
248  Q4Pub.publish(Q4Vel);
249  Q5Pub.publish(Q5Vel);
250  Q6nPub.publish(Q6nVel);
251  Q6pPub.publish(Q6pVel);
252 }
